pageContext.claim: “Judge Ken Starr, former Solicitor Generel & Independent Counsel, just stated that, after two years, ‘there is no evidence or proof of collusion’ & further that ‘there is no evidence that there was a campaign financing violation involving the President.’ Thank you Judge. @FoxNews”
pageContext.analysis: Trump tweets positive comments from Ken Starr. But the plain fact is that former Trump attorney Michael Cohen pleaded guilty to campaign finance violations that he said he made at the direction of the president.
